Package: grasslandDrought
Title: Streamlined Analysis of Grassland Drought Effects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Olivier", "Ruiz", , "hymenopteres.entomo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Wraps the nlme::lme() workflow for analyzing grassland drought
    experiments with nested random effects. Provides functions for importing
    UREP-format Excel datasets, calculating relative soil water content (RSWC)
    and climatic water balance (P-PET), running treatment x date mixed models,
    generating diagnostic plots, and exporting structured results to JSON.
    Based on the methodology of Picon-Cochard et al. (2021)
    <doi:10.24072/pcjournal.54>.
